Utilities that I got bored of writing often. Mostly string extension methods.

String extensions
Save some text to a file
"123".Save(@"C:\temp\file.txt");

Open a file
@"c:\temp\file.txt".Open(); //returns a Stream

Remove some value from a string
"%123%".Remove("%"); //returns "123"

Stream extensions
stream.ToBase64(); //returns base64 string of the given stream

Composite examples:
Open a file, then save the file as base64 to a new file
@"c:\temp\data.doc".Open().ToBase64().Save(@"c:\temp\data.txt");
